// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Audit log — two styles sharing one bounded context.
//
// AppAuditEntry is the app-wide log read by `user.role === "admin"` for
// moderation-class events (bans, impersonations, global rollouts).
//
// WorkspaceAuditEntry is tenant-scoped and read by workspace/team admins;
// `teamId` optionally narrows an entry to a specific team. Both tables
// are append-only — entries are materialized by a post-commit projector
// listening to the domain event bus.
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


